  <summary date="2020-09-15T21:32:54Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Emergency Judicial Tolling Act

This bill tolls (i.e., pauses) the statute of limitations for criminal and civil actions under federal law during the period of January 31, 2020, through December 31, 2020.</summary>
